ed echo that arises when circumstellar material Compton-scatters the\nprompt radiation and examine the spectral signatures expected from the\ninteraction of the GRB afterglow with the ejected medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Dec 2000 19:58:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Sep 2001 12:25:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
