ximation.\nThe considerable deviations in the results illustrate the inadequacy of\nemploying the semi-relativistic treatment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Dec 2000 10:31:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
